import math

def calculate_volume(side1, side2, side3):
    s = (side1 + side2 + side3) * 2
    base_area = math.sqrt(s * (s - side1) * (s - side2) * (s - side3))
    height = max(side1, side2, side3)
    volume = base_area * height
    volume = round(volume, 2)
    return volume
